      <details>
        <summary>What is a margin calculator?</summary>
        <p>A margin calculator helps investors determine the financial requirements and risks of borrowing money from a broker to purchase stock. It computes the total position value, the loan amount, and the crucial margin call price.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
